":"... I never thought a postcard I wrote to myself could put this much pressure on me.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event105-04-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"(I want to turn all of my past experiences into my strength so I can move forward.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event105-04-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"(... That's how much I value everything I've gained up until now. There are many things I should have faced head-on, but that was also my choice...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event105-04-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"Sayo","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event105-04-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharact